    ('amahle-wants-to-help', 0, $$Every time Amahle wants to help, all she hears is “NO”. Mama picks up Amahle’s toothbrush. “Mama, can I squeeze the toothpaste?” But Mama says…$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Every time Amahle wants to help, all she hears is “NO”.", "bbox": [136.4, 181.3, 430.5, 235.3], "size": 22.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Mama picks up Amahle’s toothbrush. “Mama, can I squeeze the toothpaste?”", "bbox": [81.9, 277.3, 485.0, 331.3], "size": 22.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "But Mama says…", "bbox": [197.4, 373.3, 369.5, 395.3], "size": 22.0}]$$),
