    ('amahle-wants-to-help', 10, $$Amahle grabs a book from the table. “Mama, can I read to Teddy?” And Mama says…$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Amahle grabs a book from the table. “Mama, can I read to Teddy?”", "bbox": [92.9, 213.3, 474.0, 267.3], "size": 22.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "And Mama says…", "bbox": [194.6, 309.3, 372.3, 331.3], "size": 22.0}]$$),
