    ('banzis-busy-bees', 0, $$Banzi and Gogo love to garden. Gogo’s garden has vegetables, flowers and Banzi’s favourite – bees! “Buzz-buzz,” saysBanzi.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Banzi and Gogo love to garden.", "bbox": [255.4, 72.5, 432.8, 125.2], "size": 24.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Gogo’s garden has vegetables, flowers and Banzi’s favourite – bees!", "bbox": [635.7, 69.4, 1065.1, 122.2], "size": 24.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "“Buzz-buzz,” saysBanzi.", "bbox": [622.3, 157.2, 803.7, 262.4], "size": 31.8}]$$),
    ('banzis-busy-bees', 1, $$“Buzz-buzz,” says Gogo. “Buzz-buzz,” say the bees. sunflowers The bees sit and on buzz around the garden while Banzi garden. and Gogo$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“Buzz-buzz,” says Gogo.", "bbox": [221.0, 73.2, 466.1, 152.0], "size": 27.5}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "“Buzz-buzz,” say the bees.", "bbox": [297.2, 208.8, 503.8, 308.7], "size": 31.2}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "sunflowers The bees sit and on buzz around the garden while Banzi garden. and Gogo", "bbox": [635.0, 103.4, 815.0, 271.4], "size": 24.0}]$$),
    ('banzis-busy-bees', 2, $$Banzi waves Time goodbye to leave! to each bee. “Bye-bye,sy bu Banzi bees,” says. “ Buzz-buzz,” thebeessay.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Banzi waves Time goodbye to leave! to each bee.", "bbox": [90.2, 72.6, 476.8, 154.2], "size": 24.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "“Bye-bye,sy bu Banzi bees,” says.", "bbox": [655.5, 60.4, 958.4, 178.0], "size": 32.9}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "“ Buzz-buzz,” thebeessay.", "bbox": [765.7, 272.4, 974.0, 390.2], "size": 32.3}]$$),
    ('banzis-busy-bees', 3, $$After a few days, Gogo and Banzi go to check on the garden. The bees are gone. The flowers have also disappeared!$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "After a few days, Gogo and Banzi go to check on the garden.", "bbox": [152.2, 82.6, 414.7, 164.2], "size": 24.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "The bees are gone.", "bbox": [668.9, 84.8, 881.7, 108.8], "size": 24.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "The flowers have also disappeared!", "bbox": [676.9, 142.3, 873.7, 195.2], "size": 24.0}]$$),
    ('banzis-busy-bees', 4, $$“Yho! Yho! Yho!” Banzi says. “Gogo, the bees are gone!” “Oh no!” says Gogo. “Don’t worry, I have a magic trick to call them right back!”$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“Yho! Yho! Yho!” Banzi says.", "bbox": [103.7, 74.1, 463.2, 104.1], "size": 30.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "“Gogo, the bees are gone!”", "bbox": [134.0, 136.4, 433.0, 160.4], "size": 24.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "“Oh no!” says Gogo.", "bbox": [741.9, 72.0, 958.9, 96.0], "size": 24.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "“Don’t worry, I have a magic trick to call them right back!”", "bbox": [626.9, 129.6, 1073.9, 182.4], "size": 24.0}]$$),
    ('banzis-busy-bees', 5, $$“Mmm… magic!” Banzi says. “First, we need to plant new flowers,” says Gogo. “Then, we need to leave a bucket of water in the garden.”$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“Mmm… magic!” Banzi says.", "bbox": [132.1, 68.7, 491.6, 98.7], "size": 27.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "“First, we need to plant new flowers,” says Gogo.", "bbox": [174.5, 130.9, 449.1, 183.8], "size": 24.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "“Then, we need to leave a bucket of water in the garden.”", "bbox": [630.5, 66.6, 826.5, 177.0], "size": 24.0}]$$),
    ('banzis-busy-bees', 6, $$Gogo and Banzi plant sunflower seeds and leave the bucket of water in the garden.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Gogo and Banzi plant sunflower seeds and leave the bucket of water in the garden.", "bbox": [682.0, 72.2, 1018.8, 153.8], "size": 24.0}]$$),
    ('banzis-busy-bees', 7, $$Before they leave, Gogo stands in the middle of the garden, raises up her right hand and says: “Busy, busy bees. Busy, busy bees. Come back to Banzi!” “Busy, busy bees. Busy, busy bees. Come back to me!” Banzi whispers after Gogo.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Before they leave, Gogo stands in the middle of the garden, raises up her right hand and says:", "bbox": [151.7, 77.3, 415.2, 216.6], "size": 24.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "“Busy, busy bees. Busy, busy bees. Come back to Banzi!”", "bbox": [84.1, 252.7, 482.7, 318.7], "size": 30.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "“Busy, busy bees. Busy, busy bees. Come back to me!”", "bbox": [651.0, 69.9, 1049.6, 135.9], "size": 30.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Banzi whispers after Gogo.", "bbox": [702.3, 168.2, 998.5, 192.2], "size": 24.0}]$$),
    ('banzis-busy-bees', 8, $$Banzi and Gogo check the garden every day for a week.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Banzi and Gogo check the garden every day for a week.", "bbox": [641.4, 165.4, 890.2, 247.0], "size": 24.0}]$$),
    ('banzis-busy-bees', 9, $$Nothing yet.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Nothing yet.", "bbox": [667.9, 125.6, 801.9, 149.6], "size": 24.0}]$$),
    ('banzis-busy-bees', 10, $$Nothing yet.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Nothing yet.", "bbox": [667.9, 125.6, 801.9, 149.6], "size": 24.0}]$$),
    ('banzis-busy-bees', 11, $$The bees are back! Banzi and Gogo laugh as the bees dance from flower to flower.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "The bees are back!", "bbox": [131.1, 74.8, 341.5, 98.8], "size": 24.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Banzi and Gogo laugh as the bees dance from flower to flower.", "bbox": [663.0, 74.2, 1037.8, 127.0], "size": 24.0}]$$),
    ('banzis-busy-bees', 12, $$$$, $$[]$$),
    ('banzis-busy-bees', 13, $$$$, $$[]$$),
    ('best-friends', 0, $$Zindzi and Tim Tam were best friends. They did everything together.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Zindzi and Tim Tam were best friends. They did everything together.", "bbox": [705.4, 212.8, 995.2, 317.0], "size": 25.0}]$$),
    ('best-friends', 1, $$‘Do you want to play dress-up?’ asked Oswin. ‘No thank you,’ said Zindzi. ‘I’ll play dress-up with Tim Tam.’$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "‘Do you want to play dress-up?’ asked Oswin.", "bbox": [129.0, 115.0, 437.7, 164.0], "size": 20.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "‘No thank you,’ said Zindzi. ‘I’ll play dress-up with Tim Tam.’", "bbox": [694.1, 115.0, 1006.5, 164.0], "size": 20.0}]$$),
    ('best-friends', 2, $$‘Do you want to do a puzzle with me?’ asked Kaya. ‘No thank you,’ said Zindzi. ‘I like doing puzzles with Tim Tam.’$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "‘Do you want to do a puzzle with me?’ asked Kaya.", "bbox": [299.0, 242.6, 484.0, 320.6], "size": 20.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "‘No thank you,’ said Zindzi. ‘I like doing puzzles with Tim Tam.’", "bbox": [683.3, 261.0, 1017.3, 310.0], "size": 20.0}]$$),
    ('best-friends', 3, $$‘Do you want to join our scooter race?’ asked The Twins. ‘No thank you,’ said Zindzi. ‘I’ll race with Tim Tam.’$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "‘Do you want to join our scooter race?’ asked The Twins.", "bbox": [661.3, 105.1, 1039.3, 154.1], "size": 20.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "‘No thank you,’ said Zindzi. ‘I’ll race with Tim Tam.’", "bbox": [720.6, 177.2, 980.0, 226.2], "size": 20.0}]$$),
    ('best-friends', 4, $$One day, Tim Tam didn’t come to school. ‘Tim Tam is sick,’ said Teacher. ‘Why don’t you play with your other friends, Zindzi?’$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "One day, Tim Tam didn’t come to school.", "bbox": [651.4, 174.5, 1049.1, 194.5], "size": 20.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "‘Tim Tam is sick,’ said Teacher. ‘Why don’t you play with your other friends, Zindzi?’", "bbox": [700.7, 217.7, 999.9, 295.7], "size": 20.0}]$$),
    ('best-friends', 5, $$Oswin was making a Get Well Soon card for Tim Tam. ‘But… Tim Tam is my best friend,’ said Zindzi.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Oswin was making a Get Well Soon card for Tim Tam.", "bbox": [124.7, 109.3, 442.0, 158.3], "size": 20.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "‘But… Tim Tam is my best friend,’ said Zindzi.", "bbox": [111.1, 185.9, 455.8, 245.3], "size": 20.0}]$$),
    ('best-friends', 6, $$‘You can help me,’ said Oswin. ‘Dip dip, dab dab.’ ‘Dip dip, dab dab,’ said Zindzi.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "‘You can help me,’ said Oswin. ‘Dip dip, dab dab.’ ‘Dip dip, dab dab,’ said Zindzi.", "bbox": [65.3, 126.3, 464.1, 405.9], "size": 34.1}]$$),
    ('best-friends', 7, $$When the card was done, Oswin and Zindzi played dress-up. The next day, they played hopscotch with Kaya. The day after that, the three of them rode scooters with The Twins.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "When the card was done, Oswin and Zindzi played dress-up.", "bbox": [247.0, 64.3, 492.7, 142.3], "size": 20.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "The next day, they played hopscotch with Kaya.", "bbox": [173.4, 214.2, 426.6, 263.2], "size": 20.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "The day after that, the three of them rode scooters with The Twins.", "bbox": [617.6, 64.0, 929.9, 142.0], "size": 20.0}]$$),
    ('best-friends', 8, $$On Monday, Tim Tam came back to school. ‘Let’s go read a book with Oswin!’ said Zindzi.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "On Monday, Tim Tam came back to school.", "bbox": [149.9, 112.2, 416.9, 161.2], "size": 20.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "‘Let’s go read a book with Oswin!’ said Zindzi.", "bbox": [687.4, 370.2, 1013.2, 419.2], "size": 20.0}]$$),
    ('best-friends', 9, $$‘Is Oswin your best friend now?’ asked Tim Tam. ‘He’s my new friend,’ said Zindzi. ‘He’s your friend too! Look, we made you a card.’$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "‘Is Oswin your best friend now?’ asked Tim Tam.", "bbox": [129.7, 84.5, 437.0, 133.5], "size": 20.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "‘He’s my new friend,’ said Zindzi. ‘He’s your friend too! Look, we made you a card.’", "bbox": [634.5, 75.2, 981.1, 163.7], "size": 20.0}]$$),
    ('best-friends', 10, $$‘Should we all play together?’$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "‘Should we all play together?’", "bbox": [139.3, 129.9, 427.4, 149.9], "size": 20.0}]$$),
    ('best-friends', 11, $$‘Okay,’ said Tim Tam. ‘Let’s all be best friends!’$$, $$[{"role": "SFX", "text": "‘Okay,’ said Tim Tam. ‘Let’s all be best friends!’", "bbox": [70.7, 113.6, 506.5, 184.3], "size": 28.0}]$$),
    ('best-friends', 12, $$$$, $$[]$$),
    ('best-friends', 13, $$$$, $$[]$$),
    ('brave-bora', 0, $$Bora is sitting at the clinic with Baba. Jojo, his stuffed monkey, came too. Jojo is sleeping in Bora’s bag.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Bora is sitting at the clinic with Baba.", "bbox": [71.6, 122.6, 444.3, 193.0], "size": 32.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Jojo, his stuffed monkey, came too.", "bbox": [71.6, 237.8, 415.3, 308.2], "size": 32.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Jojo is sleeping in Bora’s bag.", "bbox": [71.6, 353.0, 484.0, 385.0], "size": 32.0}]$$),
    ('brave-bora', 1, $$“I don’t like needles. They hurt!” says Bora.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“I don’t like needles. They hurt!” says Bora.", "bbox": [56.7, 245.9, 372.7, 316.4], "size": 32.0}]$$),
    ('brave-bora', 2, $$“An injection helps make you healthy. It’s okay to be scared, Bora. Baba will be right here with you. And Jojo too.”$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“An injection helps make you healthy. It’s okay to be scared, Bora. Baba will be right here with you. And Jojo too.”", "bbox": [75.1, 96.4, 454.2, 282.0], "size": 32.0}]$$),
    ('brave-bora', 3, $$“Bora Baraka!” a loud voice calls. “Let’s go Bora,” says Baba. “It’s your turn.” “Let’s come back tomorrow Baba!” says Bora.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“Bora Baraka!” a loud voice calls.", "bbox": [253.2, 128.3, 507.2, 198.7], "size": 32.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "“Let’s go Bora,” says Baba.", "bbox": [253.2, 243.5, 471.4, 313.9], "size": 32.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "“It’s your turn.”", "bbox": [253.2, 358.7, 472.1, 390.7], "size": 32.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "“Let’s come back tomorrow Baba!” says Bora.", "bbox": [675.6, 436.6, 1065.8, 507.0], "size": 32.0}]$$),
    ('brave-bora', 4, $$“Remember what Baba said you will get for being brave enough to get your injection?” asks Baba. “A red lollipop! Okay, I’m coming,” says Bora.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“Remember what Baba said you will get for being brave enough to get your injection?” asks Baba.", "bbox": [56.7, 84.4, 429.8, 231.6], "size": 32.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "“A red lollipop! Okay, I’m coming,” says Bora.", "bbox": [56.7, 390.5, 479.1, 460.9], "size": 32.0}]$$),
    ('brave-bora', 5, $$The doctor smiles at Bora. “Is this your monkey? Can we examine him too?” she asks. Bora looks at Baba, then at Jojo, and nods.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "The doctor smiles at Bora. “Is this your monkey? Can we examine him too?” she asks.", "bbox": [52.4, 57.6, 504.3, 159.6], "size": 30.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Bora looks at Baba, then at Jojo, and nods.", "bbox": [776.7, 345.2, 1055.6, 454.0], "size": 32.0}]$$),
    ('brave-bora', 6, $$“Now, it’s your turn,” she says. Will you help me give your monkey a small injection so he feels better?” asks the doctor.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“Now, it’s your turn,” she says.", "bbox": [623.6, 165.2, 1057.2, 197.2], "size": 32.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Will you help me give your monkey a small injection so he feels better?” asks the doctor.", "bbox": [623.6, 262.9, 1064.6, 371.8], "size": 32.0}]$$),
    ('brave-bora', 7, $$“TOOP!” says the doctor as she gives Jojo the monkey an injection.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“TOOP!” says the doctor as she gives Jojo the monkey an injection.", "bbox": [623.6, 134.0, 1035.5, 242.8], "size": 32.0}]$$),
    ('brave-bora', 8, $$“Now, it’s your turn. Is that a superhero on your T-shirt?” she asks. “TOOP!” she says as she gives Bora the injection.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“Now, it’s your turn. Is that a superhero on your T-shirt?” she asks.", "bbox": [623.6, 66.0, 1035.8, 174.8], "size": 32.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "“TOOP!” she says as she gives Bora the injection.", "bbox": [623.6, 431.1, 971.8, 501.5], "size": 32.0}]$$),
    ('brave-bora', 9, $$“Ouch!” shouts Bora. “Hey, that wasn’t so bad!”$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“Ouch!” shouts Bora.", "bbox": [642.0, 173.7, 940.1, 205.7], "size": 32.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "“Hey, that wasn’t so bad!”", "bbox": [642.0, 250.5, 1009.4, 282.5], "size": 32.0}]$$),
    ('brave-bora', 10, $$“I know it stings a little, but we’re done and you have been very brave!” says the doctor.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“I know it stings a little, but we’re done and you have been very brave!” says the doctor.", "bbox": [642.0, 183.6, 1039.1, 330.8], "size": 32.0}]$$),
    ('brave-bora', 11, $$“One red lollipop for our brave Bora!”$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“One red lollipop for our brave Bora!”", "bbox": [56.7, 66.0, 353.2, 136.3], "size": 32.0}]$$),
    ('brave-bora', 12, $$$$, $$[]$$),
