    ('dance-khuzwayo-dance', 0, $$Everyone knows that Khuzwayo loves to dance. When the village leader chooses him to be the next Ingoma dancer, no one is surprised.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Everyone knows that Khuzwayo loves to dance. When the village leader chooses him to be the next Ingoma dancer, no one is surprised.", "bbox": [126.4, 155.5, 440.5, 423.2], "size": 35.0}]$$),
    ('dance-khuzwayo-dance', 1, $$Ingoma is a dance to celebrate the first crops at the beginning of the year. Khuzwayo’s family is proud.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Ingoma is a dance to celebrate the first crops at the beginning of the year. Khuzwayo’s family is proud.", "bbox": [109.9, 315.1, 457.1, 498.7], "size": 35.0}]$$),
    ('dance-khuzwayo-dance', 2, $$But Khuzwayo is worried. How will he dance in front of so many people from so many villages? He normally only performs for a few neighbours.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "But Khuzwayo is worried.", "bbox": [128.3, 437.0, 438.6, 472.0], "size": 35.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "How will he dance in front of so many people from so many villages? He normally only performs for a few neighbours.", "bbox": [656.7, 174.4, 1044.0, 400.1], "size": 35.0}]$$),
    ('dance-khuzwayo-dance', 3, $$“I can’t do it! It’s too scary.” He runs away ...$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“I can’t do it! It’s too scary.”", "bbox": [191.0, 231.4, 375.9, 331.1], "size": 35.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "He", "bbox": [781.0, 154.4, 811.3, 189.4], "size": 35.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "runs", "bbox": [811.3, 219.3, 884.3, 264.3], "size": 45.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "away ...", "bbox": [885.0, 289.1, 1024.8, 344.1], "size": 55.0}]$$),
    ('dance-khuzwayo-dance', 4, $$Everyone wonders where he is. No one can find him. But Khuzwayo’s best friends know exactly where he would be!$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Everyone wonders where he is. No one can find him. But Khuzwayo’s best friends know exactly where he would be!", "bbox": [83.9, 308.7, 483.0, 492.4], "size": 35.0}]$$),
    ('dance-khuzwayo-dance', 5, $$$$, $$[]$$),
    ('dance-khuzwayo-dance', 6, $$“Why did you run away?”$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“Why did you run away?”", "bbox": [103.8, 97.3, 239.2, 250.3], "size": 45.0}]$$),
    ('dance-khuzwayo-dance', 7, $$“I am nervous. What if I make a mistake?”$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“I am nervous. What if I make a mistake?”", "bbox": [66.8, 70.1, 273.4, 206.1], "size": 40.0}]$$),
    ('dance-khuzwayo-dance', 8, $$“We can help you. Let’s all practise together!” “Khuzwayo, you’re so good. You’re ready to dance with the older dancers!”$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“We can help you. Let’s all practise together!”", "bbox": [125.7, 427.4, 441.3, 497.8], "size": 32.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "“Khuzwayo, you’re so good. You’re ready to dance with the older dancers!”", "bbox": [627.5, 427.4, 1073.3, 497.8], "size": 32.0}]$$),
    ('dance-khuzwayo-dance', 9, $$Khuzwayo grows more confident.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Khuzwayo grows more confident.", "bbox": [199.9, 311.1, 367.0, 447.1], "size": 40.0}]$$),
    ('dance-khuzwayo-dance', 10, $$On the day of the Ingoma dance Khuzwayo leads his village to the arena wearing a special outfit. He still feels a little nervous, but the rattles on his feet guide him.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "On the day of the Ingoma dance Khuzwayo leads his village to the arena wearing a special outfit.", "bbox": [56.7, 67.4, 326.4, 253.0], "size": 32.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "He still feels a little nervous, but the rattles on his feet guide him.", "bbox": [56.7, 282.1, 287.4, 429.3], "size": 32.0}]$$),
    ('dance-khuzwayo-dance', 11, $$He stomps his legs. He waves his arms. Everyone loves Khuzwayo’s dance!$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "He stomps his legs. He waves his arms. Everyone loves Khuzwayo’s dance!", "bbox": [56.7, 142.3, 357.2, 369.9], "size": 43.8}]$$),
    ('dance-khuzwayo-dance', 12, $$$$, $$[]$$),
    ('dance-khuzwayo-dance', 13, $$$$, $$[]$$),
    ('dance-mihlali', 0, $$It is almost time for the big concert at school. All the children are having fun practising. But not Mihlali …$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "It is almost time for the big concert at school. All the children are having fun practising. But not Mihlali …", "bbox": [648.2, 148.1, 1061.2, 229.7], "size": 24.0}]$$),
    ('dance-mihlali', 1, $$“I’ll help you practise at home.” She is worried she will forget her dance steps.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“I’ll help you practise at home.”", "bbox": [702.7, 148.6, 998.1, 172.6], "size": 24.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "She is worried she will forget her dance steps.", "bbox": [56.7, 415.0, 471.7, 439.0], "size": 24.0}]$$),
    ('dance-mihlali', 2, $$“I wish this concert would never happen!”$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“I wish this concert would never happen!”", "bbox": [657.3, 148.6, 1048.9, 172.6], "size": 24.0}]$$),
    ('dance-mihlali', 3, $$Not a chance! The day of the concert is getting closer…$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Not a chance! The day of the concert is getting closer…", "bbox": [90.7, 463.2, 457.0, 516.0], "size": 24.0}]$$),
    ('dance-mihlali', 4, $$GRANNY FROM “Granny has sent you a gift.”$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "GRANNY FROM", "bbox": [258.4, 293.6, 291.0, 337.1], "size": 11.7}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "“Granny has sent you a gift.”", "bbox": [147.3, 486.9, 419.6, 510.9], "size": 24.0}]$$),
    ('dance-mihlali', 5, $$GRANNY FROM Mihlali is too worried about the concert to open gifts.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "GRANNY FROM", "bbox": [228.6, 353.9, 267.8, 406.0], "size": 14.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Mihlali is too worried about the concert to open gifts.", "bbox": [788.0, 175.3, 1041.2, 228.1], "size": 24.0}]$$),
    ('dance-mihlali', 6, $$Perhaps she should take a look inside. What great dancing shoes from Granny!$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Perhaps she should take a look inside.", "bbox": [90.7, 489.5, 435.7, 513.5], "size": 24.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "What great dancing shoes from Granny!", "bbox": [651.2, 489.5, 1027.0, 513.5], "size": 24.0}]$$),
    ('dance-mihlali', 7, $$Granny was the best dancer ever.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Granny was the best dancer ever.", "bbox": [691.6, 285.4, 1011.9, 309.4], "size": 24.0}]$$),
    ('dance-mihlali', 8, $$And at home! Mihlali practises and practises at school… And she dances in her dreams.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "And at home!", "bbox": [785.8, 79.7, 915.0, 103.7], "size": 24.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Mihlali practises and practises at school…", "bbox": [90.7, 439.7, 468.7, 463.7], "size": 24.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "And she dances in her dreams.", "bbox": [709.6, 439.6, 992.6, 463.6], "size": 24.0}]$$),
    ('dance-mihlali', 9, $$Mihlali must rest. The big concert is tomorrow.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Mihlali must rest.", "bbox": [205.6, 489.6, 361.3, 513.6], "size": 24.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "The big concert is tomorrow.", "bbox": [720.4, 488.2, 980.4, 512.2], "size": 24.0}]$$),
    ('dance-mihlali', 10, $$It’s concert day. Mihlali does her dance just right. What great fun! And surprise! Granny has even come to watch Mihlali dance.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "It’s concert day. Mihlali does her dance just right. What great fun!", "bbox": [718.6, 134.9, 1076.9, 187.8], "size": 24.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "And surprise! Granny has even come to watch Mihlali dance.", "bbox": [718.6, 250.2, 1056.2, 302.9], "size": 24.0}]$$),
    ('dance-mihlali', 11, $$“I danced just like you, Granny.” “You were amazing! You are the best dancer I’ve ever seen.”$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“I danced just like you, Granny.”", "bbox": [132.1, 72.5, 434.9, 96.5], "size": 24.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "“You were amazing! You are the best dancer I’ve ever seen.”", "bbox": [657.6, 70.7, 1016.1, 123.5], "size": 24.0}]$$),
    ('dance-mihlali', 12, $$$$, $$[]$$),
    ('dance-mihlali', 13, $$$$, $$[]$$),
    ('dudus-hat', 0, $$“Hey, Dudu,” Dumisani says. “I bet you can’t throw your hat through that window.”$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“Hey, Dudu,” Dumisani says.", "bbox": [56.1, 82.1, 333.6, 112.1], "size": 25.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "“I bet you can’t throw your hat through that window.”", "bbox": [70.6, 152.1, 319.7, 252.1], "size": 30.0}]$$),
    ('dudus-hat', 1, $$Dudu looks up at the open window. It’s so high up the classroom wall, she can’t see what’s on the other side.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Dudu looks up at the open window.", "bbox": [118.2, 179.2, 448.7, 199.2], "size": 20.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "It’s so high up the classroom wall, she can’t see what’s on the other side.", "bbox": [103.9, 231.2, 463.0, 277.2], "size": 20.0}]$$),
    ('dudus-hat', 2, $$“OK,” says Dudu. “I’ll count to three.” They take their hats off and stand ready. “One...” says Dudu slowly, “two”... “THREE!”$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“OK,” says Dudu. “I’ll count to three.”", "bbox": [173.0, 92.7, 394.2, 157.7], "size": 25.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "They take their hats off and stand ready.", "bbox": [171.8, 188.8, 395.2, 234.8], "size": 20.0}, {"role": "SFX", "text": "“One...” says Dudu slowly, “two”... “THREE!”", "bbox": [642.0, 217.9, 1031.0, 441.3], "size": 68.5}]$$),
    ('dudus-hat', 3, $$Dudu and Dumisani throw their hats towards the window. Dudu’s hat lands softly against the wall and slides down onto the shelf underneath. But Dumisani’s hat gets close. It hits the windowsill and rebounds, turning three times in the air before coming to rest on the head of the stuffed rhino below.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Dudu and Dumisani throw their hats towards the window.", "bbox": [113.2, 102.2, 453.7, 148.2], "size": 20.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Dudu’s hat lands softly against the wall and slides down onto the shelf underneath.", "bbox": [118.2, 180.2, 448.7, 252.2], "size": 20.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "But Dumisani’s hat gets close. It hits the windowsill and rebounds, turning three times in the air before coming to rest on the head of the stuffed rhino below.", "bbox": [114.8, 284.2, 452.1, 408.2], "size": 20.0}]$$),
    ('dudus-hat', 4, $$Dudu and Dumisani laugh so hard, Dudu has to hold her tummy. “Again!” she says.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Dudu and Dumisani laugh so hard, Dudu has to hold her tummy.", "bbox": [121.3, 88.0, 445.7, 134.0], "size": 20.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "“Again!” she says.", "bbox": [610.0, 99.4, 863.4, 247.7], "size": 54.1}]$$),
    ('dudus-hat', 5, $$The friends fetch their hats, and Dumisani counts, “One, two, three!” Dumisani’s hat sails through the air, makes it past the windowsill, bumps against the frame and falls through the window. “YES!” he shouts. Dudu’s hat is on the shelf again.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "The friends fetch their hats, and Dumisani counts, “One, two, three!”", "bbox": [152.8, 61.8, 414.1, 143.7], "size": 25.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Dumisani’s hat sails through the air, makes it past the windowsill, bumps against the frame and falls through the window.", "bbox": [115.0, 183.8, 451.9, 281.8], "size": 20.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "“YES!” he shouts.", "bbox": [197.8, 313.7, 369.2, 343.7], "size": 20.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Dudu’s hat is on the shelf again.", "bbox": [687.2, 337.0, 837.8, 383.0], "size": 20.0}]$$),
    ('dudus-hat', 6, $$“Do it again,” Dumisani says to Dudu. Dudu gets her hat, balls it up in her hand But says her and Dumisani, hat “One, squints bounces two, at and the off three,” Dudu the window. windowsill throws. and slides down the wall again. “Again” says Dumisani.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“Do it again,” Dumisani says to Dudu. Dudu gets her hat, balls it up in her hand But says her and Dumisani, hat “One, squints bounces two, at and the off three,” Dudu the window. windowsill throws. and slides down the wall again.", "bbox": [91.3, 89.0, 475.6, 335.1], "size": 20.6}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "“Again” says Dumisani.", "bbox": [616.9, 183.0, 894.4, 318.4], "size": 20.0}]$$),
    ('dudus-hat', 7, $$“Uh uh,” says Dudu. “Let’s go outside to the swings.” She fetches her hat and puts it firmly on her head. “Ah, please, Dudu?” says Dumisani. “Here, I’ll help you.”$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“Uh uh,” says Dudu. “Let’s go outside to the swings.” She fetches her hat and puts it firmly on her head.", "bbox": [81.4, 96.3, 275.8, 273.4], "size": 21.1}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "“Ah, please, Dudu?” says Dumisani.", "bbox": [659.9, 203.0, 874.0, 258.1], "size": 25.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "“Here, I’ll help you.”", "bbox": [660.1, 290.0, 873.7, 320.0], "size": 30.0}]$$),
    ('dudus-hat', 8, $$He takes Dudu’s hat from her head, balls it up, and puts it in her hand. “Point your other hand at the window,” he says. “Now throw from your shoulder.” Dudu takes a deep breath and throws. Her hat swoops up, opens like a gliding bird, flies through the window, and disappears.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "He takes Dudu’s hat from her head, balls it up, and puts it in her hand.", "bbox": [300.1, 88.0, 502.8, 186.0], "size": 20.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "“Point your other hand at the window,” he says. “Now throw from your shoulder.” Dudu takes a deep breath and throws.", "bbox": [56.7, 288.1, 293.0, 500.1], "size": 22.2}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Her hat swoops up, opens like a gliding bird, flies through the window, and disappears.", "bbox": [654.4, 378.2, 890.5, 476.2], "size": 20.0}]$$),
    ('dudus-hat', 9, $$“Yes!” lifting Dudu and their Dumisani arms in victory. shout,$$, $$[{"role": "SFX", "text": "“Yes!”", "bbox": [139.6, 66.3, 441.2, 230.4], "size": 136.2}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "lifting Dudu and their Dumisani arms in victory. shout,", "bbox": [723.5, 133.4, 977.3, 179.4], "size": 20.0}]$$),
    ('dudus-hat', 10, $$$$, $$[]$$),
    ('dudus-hat', 11, $$“TEACHER!” Dudu shouts to Teacher Lethabo. “Our fell hats out the window!”$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“TEACHER!” Dudu shouts to Teacher Lethabo.", "bbox": [121.9, 79.6, 447.9, 221.4], "size": 49.3}, {"role": "SFX", "text": "“Our fell hats out the window!”", "bbox": [752.6, 90.1, 956.3, 215.1], "size": 41.0}]$$),
