    ('grandpa-farouks-garden', 0, $$Deep in the city, surrounded by houses and bricks and tar, you’ll find Grandpa Farouk’s garden.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Deep in the city, surrounded by houses and bricks and tar, you’ll find Grandpa Farouk’s garden.", "bbox": [751.0, 60.6, 1053.2, 121.8], "size": 18.0}]$$),
    ('grandpa-farouks-garden', 1, $$Amir visits Grandpa once a week. He loves the leaves and flowers and trees.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Amir visits Grandpa once a week. He loves the leaves and flowers and trees.", "bbox": [109.8, 120.9, 457.1, 160.5], "size": 18.0}]$$),
    ('grandpa-farouks-garden', 2, $$He helps with the compost, and works with his Grandpa all day. Amir helps to water the plants.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "He helps with the compost, and works with his Grandpa all day.", "bbox": [660.7, 60.6, 1040.1, 100.2], "size": 18.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Amir helps to water the plants.", "bbox": [157.5, 496.1, 409.4, 514.1], "size": 18.0}]$$),
    ('grandpa-farouks-garden', 3, $$When they finish, they feast on a harvest of fruit. One day, Grandpa didn’t eat his pear. “What’s wrong?” asked Amir.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "When they finish, they feast on a harvest of fruit.", "bbox": [187.1, 306.4, 379.9, 367.6], "size": 18.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "One day, Grandpa didn’t eat his pear. “What’s wrong?” asked Amir.", "bbox": [696.9, 474.5, 1003.9, 514.1], "size": 18.0}]$$),
    ('grandpa-farouks-garden', 4, $$“My garden is dying,” replied Grandpa. “Why?” asked Amir. “Look closely,” said Grandpa. “Some pests are eating the plants.”$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“My garden is dying,” replied Grandpa.", "bbox": [125.4, 164.4, 441.5, 182.4], "size": 18.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "“Why?” asked Amir.", "bbox": [204.2, 207.6, 362.7, 225.6], "size": 18.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "“Look closely,” said Grandpa. “Some pests are eating the plants.”", "bbox": [135.1, 250.8, 431.8, 290.4], "size": 18.0}]$$),
    ('grandpa-farouks-garden', 5, $$“We need ladybirds!” said Grandpa. “They are the bugs that eat the pests that kill the plants. Without ladybirds, the garden will die.” “I’ll bring you a bug or two,” said Amir.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“We need ladybirds!” said Grandpa. “They are the bugs that eat the pests that kill the plants. Without ladybirds, the garden will die.”", "bbox": [94.8, 61.3, 472.2, 122.5], "size": 18.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "“I’ll bring you a bug or two,” said Amir.", "bbox": [692.8, 496.1, 1008.0, 515.7], "size": 18.0}]$$),
    ('grandpa-farouks-garden', 6, $$For a whole week, Amir looked and searched and collected. He found one ladybird on the sports field.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "For a whole week, Amir looked and searched and collected.", "bbox": [98.2, 60.6, 468.7, 100.2], "size": 18.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "He found one ladybird on the sports field.", "bbox": [679.1, 496.1, 1021.7, 514.1], "size": 18.0}]$$),
    ('grandpa-farouks-garden', 7, $$Two more at the shop. Three at the park.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Two more at the shop.", "bbox": [191.9, 60.6, 375.0, 78.6], "size": 18.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Three at the park.", "bbox": [776.8, 496.1, 924.0, 514.1], "size": 18.0}]$$),
    ('grandpa-farouks-garden', 8, $$And four behind the TV. Next week, Amir went to visit Grandpa Farouk, and showed him his jar of ten bugs. “You’ve done well, oh my boy, you’ve done well,” Grandpa said, with a tear in his eye.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "And four behind the TV.", "bbox": [185.7, 60.6, 381.2, 78.6], "size": 18.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Next week, Amir went to visit Grandpa Farouk, and showed him his jar of ten bugs.", "bbox": [659.7, 409.7, 1041.1, 449.3], "size": 18.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "“You’ve done well, oh my boy, you’ve done well,” Grandpa said, with a tear in his eye.", "bbox": [675.5, 474.5, 1025.3, 514.1], "size": 18.0}]$$),
    ('grandpa-farouks-garden', 9, $$Grandpa was very happy. The ladybirds were very hungry!$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Grandpa was very happy.", "bbox": [105.9, 76.0, 319.3, 94.0], "size": 18.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "The ladybirds were very hungry!", "bbox": [79.4, 119.2, 345.9, 137.2], "size": 18.0}]$$),
    ('grandpa-farouks-garden', 10, $$The ladybirds ate the pests, and the garden blossomed.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "The ladybirds ate the pests, and the garden blossomed.", "bbox": [168.6, 244.9, 465.0, 284.5], "size": 18.0}]$$),
    ('grandpa-farouks-garden', 11, $$From that day on, Grandpa Farouk’s garden did what gardens should do. It grew and grew and grew.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "From that day on, Grandpa Farouk’s garden did what gardens should do.", "bbox": [781.6, 98.1, 1082.1, 137.7], "size": 18.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "It grew and grew and grew.", "bbox": [818.7, 162.9, 1045.0, 180.9], "size": 18.0}]$$),
    ('grandpa-farouks-garden', 12, $$$$, $$[]$$),
    ('grandpa-farouks-garden', 13, $$$$, $$[]$$),
    ('grumpy-cloud', 0, $$In a colourful land filled with feelings, there lived a boy named Fafa.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "In a colourful land filled with feelings, there lived a boy named Fafa.", "bbox": [114.9, 136.6, 452.0, 277.4], "size": 28.1}]$$),
    ('grumpy-cloud', 1, $$Fafa was a cheerful boy who loved to run and play all day.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Fafa was a cheerful boy who loved to run and play all day.", "bbox": [128.9, 258.1, 438.0, 390.9], "size": 26.0}]$$),
    ('grumpy-cloud', 2, $$But he had a special gift: his feelings could come to life.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "But he had a special gift: his feelings could come to life.", "bbox": [679.8, 253.2, 1021.0, 355.2], "size": 30.0}]$$),
    ('grumpy-cloud', 3, $$One day, Fafa woke up feeling grumpy. Grumpy Cloud, with a frown on their face, followed Fafa around all day.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "One day, Fafa woke up feeling grumpy. Grumpy Cloud, with a frown on their face, followed Fafa around all day.", "bbox": [92.2, 190.9, 474.7, 364.9], "size": 30.0}]$$),
    ('grumpy-cloud', 4, $$Whenever Fafa tried to play, Grumpy Cloud would make everything sad.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Whenever Fafa tried to play, Grumpy Cloud would make everything sad.", "bbox": [652.3, 130.7, 1048.5, 232.7], "size": 30.0}]$$),
    ('grumpy-cloud', 5, $$Fafa tried his best to shake off Grumpy Cloud... but nothing worked.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Fafa tried his best to shake off Grumpy Cloud...", "bbox": [667.6, 315.6, 1040.3, 381.6], "size": 30.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "but nothing worked.", "bbox": [764.5, 425.3, 1040.3, 455.3], "size": 30.0}]$$),
    ('grumpy-cloud', 6, $$He tried dancing, but Grumpy Cloud was STILL there.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "He tried dancing, but Grumpy Cloud was STILL there.", "bbox": [138.8, 239.5, 428.1, 341.5], "size": 30.0}]$$),
    ('grumpy-cloud', 7, $$Mama decided to tickle Grumpy Cloud. It DIDN’T work.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Mama decided to tickle Grumpy Cloud.", "bbox": [712.6, 201.5, 1036.4, 267.5], "size": 30.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "It DIDN’T work.", "bbox": [768.1, 297.9, 980.8, 327.9], "size": 30.0}]$$),
    ('grumpy-cloud', 8, $$Mama tried again and Grumpy Cloud smiled slightly, but Grumpy Cloud stayed.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Mama tried again and Grumpy Cloud smiled slightly, but Grumpy Cloud stayed.", "bbox": [102.5, 183.1, 464.4, 324.4], "size": 30.0}]$$),
    ('grumpy-cloud', 9, $$Mama tickled Grumpy Cloud one last time. A giggle came out and Grumpy Cloud went away.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Mama tickled Grumpy Cloud one last time. A giggle came out and Grumpy Cloud went away.", "bbox": [55.3, 127.1, 503.1, 229.1], "size": 30.0}]$$),
    ('grumpy-cloud', 10, $$Fafa laughed with joy and a happy little smile appeared.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Fafa laughed with joy and a happy little smile appeared.", "bbox": [668.4, 221.1, 1032.4, 323.1], "size": 30.0}]$$),
    ('grumpy-cloud', 11, $$Fafa knew that it was okay to have different feelings, as long as he knew his way back to his smile.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Fafa knew that it was okay to have different feelings,", "bbox": [93.0, 101.6, 473.9, 224.9], "size": 37.5}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "as long as he knew his way back to his smile.", "bbox": [668.2, 101.4, 1032.6, 165.2], "size": 29.0}]$$),
    ('grumpy-cloud', 12, $$$$, $$[]$$),
    ('grumpy-cloud', 13, $$$$, $$[]$$),
    ('hello', 0, $$My name is Lolo. I have many friends. Come out with me to say hello!$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "My name is Lolo. I have many friends. Come out with me to say hello!", "bbox": [85.0, 186.0, 357.2, 372.0], "size": 36.0}]$$),
    ('hello', 1, $$Hello Sun, big and bright. You fill the day with your bright light.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Hello Sun, big and bright. You fill the day with your bright light.", "bbox": [85.0, 186.0, 366.5, 372.0], "size": 36.0}]$$),
    ('hello', 2, $$Hello Grass, soft and green. You give us all a place to play.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Hello Grass, soft and green. You give us all a place to play.", "bbox": [85.0, 194.0, 294.9, 380.0], "size": 36.0}]$$),
    ('hello', 3, $$Hello Sky, broad and blue. You fill the sky with the colour blue.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Hello Sky, broad and blue. You fill the sky with the colour blue.", "bbox": [85.0, 194.0, 354.1, 380.0], "size": 36.0}]$$),
    ('hello', 4, $$Hello Moon, up in the dark. You make the night not so dark.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Hello Moon, up in the dark. You make the night not so dark.", "bbox": [85.0, 194.0, 345.5, 380.0], "size": 36.0}]$$),
    ('hello', 5, $$Hello Star, big and white. You make the night so very nice.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Hello Star, big and white. You make the night so very nice.", "bbox": [85.0, 194.0, 345.5, 380.0], "size": 36.0}]$$),
    ('hello', 6, $$Hello Wind, strong and free. You blow things around, and make it cool.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Hello Wind, strong and free. You blow things around, and make it cool.", "bbox": [85.0, 194.0, 409.6, 380.0], "size": 36.0}]$$),
    ('hello', 7, $$Hello Rain, pouring down. You bring water, and cool our ground.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Hello Rain, pouring down. You bring water, and cool our ground.", "bbox": [85.0, 194.0, 367.6, 380.0], "size": 36.0}]$$),
    ('hello', 8, $$Hello Lightning, from high above. Your bright flashing light gives us a fright. Hello Thunder, roaring in the rain. You make a boom noise, so very loud.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Hello Lightning, from high above. Your bright flashing light gives us a fright.", "bbox": [85.0, 69.4, 412.6, 255.4], "size": 36.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Hello Thunder, roaring in the rain. You make a boom noise, so very loud.", "bbox": [85.0, 319.4, 419.9, 505.4], "size": 36.0}]$$),
    ('hello', 9, $$Hello Dew, drops of water. You make the ground soft and wet.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Hello Dew, drops of water. You make the ground soft and wet.", "bbox": [85.0, 194.0, 374.6, 380.0], "size": 36.0}]$$),
    ('hello', 10, $$Hello Tree, big and strong. You give us shade and fruit to eat.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Hello Tree, big and strong. You give us shade and fruit to eat.", "bbox": [85.0, 194.0, 326.2, 380.0], "size": 36.0}]$$),
    ('hello', 11, $$Hello Bird, flying in the sky. You fill our days with lovely songs.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Hello Bird, flying in the sky. You fill our days with lovely songs.", "bbox": [85.0, 194.0, 315.2, 380.0], "size": 36.0}]$$),
    ('hello', 12, $$hello!$$, $$[{"role": "SFX", "text": "hello!", "bbox": [1032.0, 482.3, 1078.0, 511.5], "size": 17.8}]$$),
    ('hello', 13, $$Hello You, reading this book. Now you’ve met my friends, please show me yours!$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Hello You, reading this book.", "bbox": [90.4, 56.1, 476.5, 92.1], "size": 36.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Now you’ve met my friends, please show me yours!", "bbox": [95.4, 432.7, 471.5, 513.7], "size": 36.0}]$$),
